applicationFailedToLoadError.comment:
[Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-SPApplicationBase] An error to show when the application fails to load in the page start.
    {0} is the application id.

applicationFailedToLoadWithMessageError.comment:
[Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-SPApplicationBase] An error to show when the application fails to load in the page start. It includes the error message.
    {0} is the application id, {1} is the original error.
applicationFailedToLoadWithMessageError.value:
Application failed to load. Id: "{0}".
Error: {1}

applicationFailedToInitializeError.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-SPApplicationBase] An error to show when the applicaiton fails to initialize. The {0} placeholder is the error.
